461
00:34:07,275 --> 00:34:08,609
Ayan na!

462
00:34:08,693 --> 00:34:09,944
Sige. Sa pagkakataong ito,

463
00:34:10,027 --> 00:34:14,866
Kami ang magpapasya
kung sino ang may pinakamalakas na braso sa aming nayon.

464
00:34:14,949 --> 00:34:17,577
Sinumang nakakaramdam ng malakas
sa loob ng kanilang nayon

465
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:19,579
maaaring humakbang at tumugon sa hamon.

466
00:34:19,662 --> 00:34:21,455
Lumabas ka!

467
00:34:22,331 --> 00:34:23,332
Tara na, tara na!

468
00:34:27,378 --> 00:34:29,380
Yumuko upang batiin ang isa't isa.

469
00:34:30,173 --> 00:34:31,507
Sige. Maghawak-kamay tayo.

470
00:34:32,508 --> 00:34:34,302
Kumapit nang mahigpit.

471
00:34:36,137 --> 00:34:36,971
Matigas siya!

472
00:34:37,054 --> 00:34:39,473
Kwang-mo, ayokong saktan ang pride mo,

473
00:34:39,557 --> 00:34:41,559
kaya maghihintay ako ng limang segundo bago manalo.

474
00:34:41,642 --> 00:34:43,227
Kalimutan mo na 'yan. Gawin mo na lang ang makakaya mo.

475
00:34:43,311 --> 00:34:44,145
Huwag kang matakot.

476
00:34:44,228 --> 00:34:45,354
Kumapit nang mahigpit.

477
00:34:45,438 --> 00:34:46,981
Handa, handa na, umalis na!

478
00:34:48,274 --> 00:34:49,192
Kaya mo 'yan!

479
00:34:50,401 --> 00:34:54,280
Kaya mo 'yan!

480
00:35:00,828 --> 00:35:01,662
